name: AI Imagined CryptoPunk #2
description:
Self-portrait as my CryptoPunk.
Three years ago, my first works on
SuperRare were portraits painted by
my robot after training on 10,000
celebrity faces. This work used the
exact handwritten algorithm except
that it trained on the 10,000
CryptoPunks with results weighted to
favor traits of mine, punk#3421.
